<div class="page">

  <div class="hero">
    <div class="eyebrow"><div class="dot"></div>Waitlist Wars &middot; NZ Only</div>
    <div class="headline">
      <span class="w1">Who's got</span>
      <span class="w2">NZ's most</span>
      <span class="w3">loyal crew?</span>
    </div>
    <p class="sub1">I am one mum from Tauranga doing this completely on my own. No investors. No team. No ad budget. Every spare hour I have goes into this.</p>
