  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="slabel">The prize</div>
    <div class="prize-wrap">
      <div class="prize-bar"></div>
      <div class="prize-inner">
        <div class="prize-title">&#x1F3C6; Both winners get this</div>
        <div class="prize-divider"></div>
        <div class="prize-item"><div class="prize-dot"></div><div><strong>Permanent founding credit</strong><p>Named on StreamStack.co.nz as a Waitlist Wars champion. Forever.</p></div></div>
        <div class="prize-item"><div class="prize-dot"></div><div><strong>Free first year of StreamStack</strong><p>On the house when we launch.</p></div></div>
        <div class="prize-item"><div class="prize-dot"></div><div><strong>Early access</strong><p>In before the public opens.</p></div></div>
        <div class="prize-item"><div class="prize-dot"></div><div><strong>Bragging rights</strong><p>Proof your community shows up when it counts. That is everything.</p></div></div>
        <p class="no-cash">No cash. No vouchers. No gift cards. Clout only.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="section">
    <div class="slabel">Live leaderboard</div>
    <a href="https://streamstack.co.nz#refer" class="lb-point">
      <div>
        <strong>Watch the rankings move in real time</strong>
        <p>Leaderboard lives on the main StreamStack site</p>
      </div>
      <div class="lb-arrow">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polyline points="9 18 15 12 9 6"/></svg>
      </div>
