  <div class="section">
    <div class="cta-block">
      <h2>Ready to enter?</h2>
      <p>Sign up to the waitlist and you'll get your unique referral link instantly.<br>Share it. Every Kiwi through your link is a point on the leaderboard.</p>
      <a href="https://streamstack.co.nz#waitlist" class="cta-btn">Get my referral link</a>
      <p class="cta-note">Takes 10 seconds. NZ creators only. Your stats appear publicly on the leaderboard.<br>No cash prize. Competition closes at StreamStack launch.</p>
